**Whispers** | Ability Type
__Basics__
Whispering is a type of ability that allows roles to anonymously communicate in some way. Whispering abilities are immune to redirection.

For a complete list of roles with whisper abilities, check `$i whispers list`.
__Details__
Examles: The Bartender may anonymously send messages in public, while roles such as the Corrupt Wolf can anonymously communicate with one player of their choice each day.
The Whispering ability is activated at the start of the anonymous communication and stops when the anonymous communication ends.
